#Text=Girl with umbrella says : " Wow , great make - up . "
#Text=Toph says : " Thanks . "
#Text=Girl with umbrella says : " For a clown ! "
#Text=Katara says : " Do n't listen to them , let 's just keep walking . "
#Text=Star says : " I think she looks cute .
#Text=" Katara says : " Let 's go , Toph .
#Text=" Toph says : " No , no , that was a good one .
#Text=Like your poodle monkey .
#Text=You know what else is a good one ?
#Text=" Katara says : " Now that was funny .
#Text=" Katara says : " Those girls do n't know what they 're talking about .
#Text=" Toph says : " It 's okay .
#Text=One of the good things about being blind , is I do n't have to waste my time worrying about appearance .
#Text=I do n't care what I look like .
#Text=I 'm not looking for anyone 's approval .
#Text=I know who I am .
#Text=" Katara says : " That 's what I really admire about you , Toph .
#Text=You 're so strong , and confident , and self - assured .
#Text=And I know it does n't matter , but ... You 're really pretty .
#Text=" Toph says : " I am ?
#Text=" Katara says : " Yeah , you are .
#Text=" Toph says : " I 'd return the compliment , but I 've no idea how you look like .
#Text=Thank you , Katara .
#Text=" Katara says : " Ow !
#Text="
